OL,3,CMan guilty of PC Beshenivsky's murder
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FThe mastermind of an armed robbery
OL,7,Fthat ended in a police officer being
OL,8,Fshot dead has died in jail, less than
OL,9,Fa year after he was sentenced.
OL,11,FPiran Ditta Khan was jailed last May,
OL,12,Fbecoming the final member of the gang
OL,13,Fresponsible for the armed raid which
OL,14,Fended in PC Sharon Beshenivsky's
OL,15,Fmurder to be convicted having spent
OL,16,Fnearly 15 years on the run.
