OL,3,CMan guilty of PC Beshenivsky's murder
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FA Prison Service spokesperson
OL,7,Fconfirmed his death on Friday, saying:
OL,8,F"HMP Wakefield prisoner Piran Ditta
OL,9,FKhan died on Friday February 21. As
OL,10,Fwith all deaths in custody, the Prison
OL,11,Fand Probation Ombudsman will
OL,12,Finvestigate."
OL,14,FPC Beshenivsky was murdered on her
OL,15,Fdaughter's fourth birthday while
OL,16,Finterrupting a robbery at family-run
OL,17,FUniversal Express travel agents in
OL,18,FBradford, West Yorkshire, in November
OL,19,F2005.
