OL,3,CMan guilty of PC Beshenivsky's murder
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FThe 76-year-old was found guilty at
OL,7,FLeeds Crown Court of murdering PC
OL,8,FBeshenivsky, as well as two counts of
OL,9,Fpossession of a firearm with intent to
OL,10,Fendanger life and two counts of
OL,11,Fpossession of a prohibited weapon.
OL,13,FLast May, Mr Justice Hilliard jailed
OL,14,FKhan for life with a minimum term of
OL,15,F40 years.
OL,17,FDuring his trial, jurors heard Khan
OL,18,Fwas the only one of the group who was
OL,19,Ffamiliar with Universal Express and
OL,20,Fhad used the firm in the past to send
OL,21,Fmoney to family in Pakistan.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
