OL,3,CMan guilty of PC Beshenivsky's murder
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FHe flew to Pakistan two months after
OL,7,FPC Beshenivsky's death and remained at
OL,8,Fliberty there until he was arrested by
OL,9,FPakistani authorities in January 2020
OL,10,Fand then extradited to the UK in 2023.
OL,12,FSentencing him last year, Mr Justice
OL,13,FHilliard told Khan: "You will
OL,14,Finevitably spend the remainder of your
OL,15,Flife in custody, but that is a
OL,16,Fconsequence of sentencing a man of
OL,17,Fyour age for a crime of this
OL,18,Fparticular gravity."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
