OL,3,CMan guilty of PC Beshenivsky's murder
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FIn a statement to the court, Paul
OL,7,FBeshenivsky, who had been married to
OL,8,FPC Beshenivsky for four years when she
OL,9,Fdied, said: "The way we lost Sharon
OL,10,Fwas in the most brutal, callous and
OL,11,Ffutile way.
OL,13,F"She never came home due to the
OL,14,Factions and organisation of one person
OL,15,F- Piran Ditta Khan."
